    <Contribution_English/>
    <Contribution_Welsh/>
    <contribution_verbatim>Will the Cabinet Secretary make a statement on the reliability of bus services in rural communities? Constituents in Aberdwynant report that the last evening service now leaves before many shift workers finish, and that weekend provision has effectively disappeared.</contribution_verbatim>
