    <Member_Sortcode>FIX9903</Member_Sortcode>
    <Contribution_English/>
    <Contribution_Welsh/>
    <contribution_verbatim>I thank the Member for that question. Bus reliability in rural areas is a priority for this Government. We have allocated an additional 12 million pounds this year to the bus network grant, and franchising powers under the recent legislation will, for the first time, let us plan rural routes around passengers rather than around commercial viability alone.</contribution_verbatim>
