    <Contribution_English/>
    <Contribution_Welsh/>
    <contribution_verbatim>Dros y degawd diwethaf collwyd un o bob tri llwybr gwledig. Nid ystadegyn yw hynny: mae'n golygu apwyntiadau ysbyty a gollwyd, swyddi na ellir eu cymryd, a phentrefi sy'n gwagio.</contribution_verbatim>
    <contribution_translated>Over the last decade one in three rural routes has been lost. That is not a statistic: it means missed hospital appointments, jobs that cannot be taken, and villages that are emptying.</contribution_translated>
