    <Member_Sortcode>FIX9902</Member_Sortcode>
    <Contribution_English/>
    <Contribution_Welsh/>
    <contribution_verbatim>I rise to support the motion. The evidence from my constituency is stark: a single missed connection in Aberdwynant can strand a passenger for four hours. Franchising must come with a guarantee of minimum service levels — frequency floors, first and last bus times, and integrated ticketing with rail.</contribution_verbatim>
