    <Member_Sortcode>FIX9903</Member_Sortcode>
    <Contribution_English/>
    <Contribution_Welsh/>
    <contribution_verbatim>The Government will support the motion as amended. Let me be clear about what franchising can and cannot do. It cannot conjure drivers we do not have — recruitment remains the binding constraint — but it can end the situation where a profitable urban corridor is run by one operator while the rural feeder that fills it is abandoned by another.</contribution_verbatim>
